    <div class="help-center">
      <h2 class="faq-title">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
      <div class="faq">
        <div class="faq-item">
          <div class="faq-question" onclick="toggleAnswer('answer1')">
            <span class="faq-plus">+</span> What is Scholar's Lore?
          </div>
          <div class="faq-answer" id="answer1" style="display: none;">
            Scholar's Lore is an online learning platform that offers a variety of courses to enhance your educational journey.
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item">
          <div class="faq-question" onclick="toggleAnswer('answer2')">
            <span class="faq-plus">+</span> What type of courses are available on Scholar's Lore?
          </div>
          <div class="faq-answer" id="answer2" style="display: none;">
            We offer a wide range of courses beyond class 12, including technical, competitive exam preparation, and skill-development programs tailored for college students and professionals.
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item">
          <div class="faq-question" onclick="toggleAnswer('answer3')">
            <span class="faq-plus">+</span> Is there any customer support available?
          </div>
          <div class="faq-answer" id="answer3" style="display: none;">
            Yes, our customer support team is available 24/7 to assist you with any issues or questions you may have.
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item">
          <div class="faq-question" onclick="toggleAnswer('answer4')">
            <span class="faq-plus">+</span> How do I register on Scholar's Lore?
          </div>
          <div class="faq-answer" id="answer4" style="display: none;">
            You can register easily using your email address, or save time by signing in with your Google account through our secure login system.
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item">
          <div class="faq-question" onclick="toggleAnswer('answer5')">
            <span class="faq-plus">+</span> Are the courses free or paid?
          </div>
          <div class="faq-answer" id="answer5" style="display: none;">
            Some of the courses are free, while others may require a subscription or one-time payment. Please check the course details for more information.
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item">
          <div class="faq-question" onclick="toggleAnswer('answer6')">
            <span class="faq-plus">+</span> Are there any prerequisites for taking a course?
          </div>
          <div class="faq-answer" id="answer6" style="display: none;">
            Some advanced courses may have recommended prerequisites, which are mentioned in the course description. However, many of our courses are beginner-friendly and open to everyone.
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item">
          <div class="faq-question" onclick="toggleAnswer('answer7')">
            <span class="faq-plus">+</span> Can I access the platform on mobile devices?
          </div>
          <div class="faq-answer" id="answer7" style="display: none;">
            Yes, Scholar’s Lore is fully responsive and mobile-friendly, so you can learn anytime, anywhere on your phone or tablet.
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item">
          <div class="faq-question" onclick="toggleAnswer('answer8')">
            <span class="faq-plus">+</span> Is there any support available if I face technical issues?
          </div>
          <div class="faq-answer" id="answer8" style="display: none;">
            Definitely. You can reach out to our support team via the "Contact Us" page, and we’ll assist you as soon as possible.
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item">
          <div class="faq-question" onclick="toggleAnswer('answer9')">
            <span class="faq-plus">+</span> What should I do if a video or lesson isn’t loading?
          </div>
          <div class="faq-answer" id="answer9" style="display: none;">
            Try refreshing the page or checking your internet connection. If the problem persists, contact our support team through the Help Center.
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- New FAQ Question -->
        <div class="faq-item">
          <div class="faq-question" onclick="toggleAnswer('answer10')">
            <span class="faq-plus">+</span> Is my personal information safe on Scholar’s Lore?
          </div>
          <div class="faq-answer" id="answer10" style="display: none;">
            We prioritize your privacy and use encryption and secure protocols to ensure your data is always protected.
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <p class="powered-by-text">Powered by Scholar's Lore, an innovative online learning platform dedicated to enhancing your educational journey.</p>
    </div>
